# Internationalization

## Rules
- No hardcoded text - use `t()` for all user-visible text
- TR and EN must stay in sync
- Backend returns i18n keys, not raw text

## Usage
```vue
const { t } = useI18n()
{{ t('common.save') }}
```

## Error Handling
```typescript
import { translateError } from '@/i18n'
toast.error(translateError(error.message))
```
